title: Samsung Galaxy Watch 5 ‘Pro’ gets further confirmation through codename leak
content:
The Galaxy Watch 5 series is set to debut in the coming months and some recent rumors suggested that a “Pro” model was on its way. Now, another leak supports the existence of the Galaxy Watch 5 “Pro,” and clears up the branding that Samsung will use.

more…

The post Samsung Galaxy Watch 5 ‘Pro’ gets further confirmation through codename leak appeared first on 9to5Google.
description: A leak detailing the codenames and model numbers of Samsung's next batch of smartwatches all but confirms the "Galaxy Watch 5 Pro" is coming.
